### LOGOUT
### ========================================
POST {{authUrl}}/logout
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
# Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### ========================================
### CHECK SESSION SETELAH LOGOUT
### ========================================
GET {{authUrl}}/me
